{"id": 2513, "genre": 1000, "title": "日常交流中，你都遭遇过哪些“开场白”的困扰？", "description": "“Hello！呃……Bye！”（图片来自：iStock ©️CSA-Images）", "record_count": 15646, "comment_count": 38, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180911180042g4ZJHyKC8TljAsP9.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-13T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4666, "title": "日常交流中，你都遭遇过哪些“开场白”的困扰？", "content": "日常交流中，你都遭遇过哪些“开场白”的困扰？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 297992, "content": "陌生人搭话时没话找话说，不是尬聊天气就是聊家乡", "image": "img/option/option/20180911174719P2gtWiYEyD9XJpnh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298199, "content": "跟周围半生不熟的人通常都是打完招呼就拜拜", "image": "img/option/option/20180911175424EBb7QX4pH10ofVzW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 297998, "content": "进一个群没啥好说的，只能发发表情活跃气氛", "image": "img/option/option/20180911180100t2EvUQ0JrbZdADN5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298191, "content": "逢年过节开场白“过年好过年好”后面就只会接傻笑", "image": "img/option/option/20180911175432DJWjzMl6rCOAb9w1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298197, "content": "被不熟的人称呼“亲爱的、宝宝、小姐姐、xx哥”", "image": "img/option/option/20180911174948iyE7YZ9CcGb3LSMv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298198, "content": "搭讪时被直接问“可不可以交个朋友”、“加个微信”", "image": "img/option/option/201809111753364SJl06WamT2rAPnK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298200, "content": "明明不熟，冒出一句“在干嘛呢”就很吓人", "image": "img/option/option/20180911175717WFKl1ISXq7YJLh6B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298232, "content": "“在吗”打招呼之后就不说事了", "image": "img/option/option/20180911175710nd4sh23VBbL85qzO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}